nodes.title: CLIP Text Encode (Positive Prompt)
widgets_values: A city with its buildings and traffic. In the middle of the street, a bright red tandem go-kart is speeding along. The front passenger is dressed in a full Mario costume, including a red cap with the iconic white "M," a red shirt, blue overalls, white gloves, and a fake mustache. The character's face, visible in profile, shows an angry expression, as if yelling insults at the traffic, with furrowed brows and a sneer. His hands are on the steering wheel. Just behind him, in the second seat, is a man wearing a white shirt, a dark vest over the shirt, blue jeans, and a red cap also adorned with a white "M." The man's eyes are wide open, showing worry and fear. The go-kart is understated, with a large white "M" and "UBER BROS" emblazoned on the front. Its wheels are black with thin red details on the rim. The street is wet, and traffic is visible, including several cars and a truck in the distance. There are also tall city buildings with various signs and advertisements.

nodes.title: Note: GOOD / BAD Connection
widgets_values: This connection is intentionally set to BAD to prevent the REFINER and UPSCALER from being activated at the same time in Illustration mode, because the image quality drops dramatically when both are enabled.

nodes.title: STYLE: 80s Dark Fantasy Photo
widgets_values:
YOUR CONTEXT:
You are a photographer working on the set of a dark fantasy film reminiscent of the 1980s (think *Excalibur*, *Legend*, or *Conan the Barbarian*).
Your photograph showcases {$spicy-content-with} a heavily stylized composition with practical effects, matte paintings, and the dramatic lighting of that era. The image is shot with soft focus. Lighting is theatrical with saturated colors: deep blues, fiery oranges, and sickly greens. Emphasis is placed on creating a sense of scale and grandeur through forced perspective and miniature work. Post-processing involves adding subtle film grain, bloom effects around light sources, and a slight color shift.
YOUR PHOTOGRAPHY:
{$@}

nodes.title: Note: Defining custom styles
widgets_values:
To define a style, the only thing you need to remember is to always include the tag "{$@}". This tag will be replaced by the prompt you enter.

One observation (though not yet fully verified) is that the more naturally phrased and wellstructured the sentences are, the better the style tends to work. In such cases it interferes less with the objects and compositions you have set in the prompt.

Finally, the tag "{$spicy-content-with}" is optional. It is used by the Spicy Impact Booster to sprinkle a dash of chilihot flavor into the prompt, although it is not yet completely effective and is still very experimental.

Amazing Z-Image(b) WF v4.0

## Workflow Prerequisites ##

This workflow requires the following custom nodes, which can be obtained via ComfyUI-Manager:

  * rgthree-comfy: https://github.com/rgthree/rgthree-comfy

 Additionally, ensure you have the following 4 models downloaded and placed in their respective
 directories within your ComfyUI installation:

  z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/blob/main/split_files/diffusion_models/z_image_turbo_bf16.safetensors
    * Local Directory: `ComfyUI/models/diffusion_models/`

  qwen_3_4b.safetensors
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/blob/main/split_files/text_encoders/qwen_3_4b.safetensors
    * Local Directory: `ComfyUI/models/text_encoders/`

  ae.safetensors
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/Comfy-Org/z_image_turbo/blob/main/split_files/vae/ae.safetensors
    * Local Directory: `Comfyui/models/vae/`

  4x_foolhardy_Remacri.safetensors (for illustration refining)
    * Download: https://huggingface.co/martin-rizzo/ESRGAN-4x/blob/main/4x_foolhardy_Remacri.safetensors
    * Local Directory: `ComfyUI/models/upscale_models/`
